  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Create customers Copy",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "id": "6e6c0c4c-acb2-4098-8b0a-c3756607a641",
            "exec": [
              "let myVar = pm.collectionVariables.get(\"customer-id\");",
              "myVar ++ // increment by 1",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"customer-id\", myVar);",
              ""
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "packages": {}
          }
        }
      ],
      "id": "a6bc4962-6364-428b-968e-1f839fac368d",
      "protocolProfileBehavior": {
        "disableBodyPruning": true
      },
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Auth-Token",
            "value": "{{token}}",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "[\r\n    {\r\n        \"email\": \"customer+{{customer-id}}@mybigcommerce.com\",\r\n        \"first_name\": \"Customer {{customer-id}}\",\r\n        \"last_name\": \"Shopper\",\r\n        \"customer_group_id\": {{customer-id}}\r\n    }\r\n]"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://api.bigcommerce.com/stores/{{store_hash}}/v3/customers",
          "protocol": "https",
          "host": [
            "api",
            "bigcommerce",
            "com"
          ],
          "path": [
            "stores",
            "{{store_hash}}",
            "v3",
            "customers"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Creates customers. Multiple customers can be created in one call.\n\n## Required Fields\n* first_name\n* last_name\n* email\n\n## Required Fields Customer Address\n* first_name\n* last_name\n* address1\n* city\n* state_or_province\n* country_code\n* postal_code\n\n## Required Fields Attributes\nAttributes must be created BEFORE creating a customer.\n* attribute_id\n* attribute_value – This is input as a string, regardless of the Type.\n\n## Notes \nFor multi-storefront merchants who wants to give:\n\n* Global access:\n * The channel listed in `origin_channel_id` needs `allow_global_logins=true` in their channel settings\n * Leave `channel_ids` empty\n* Channel restricted access:\n * The channel listed in `origin_channel_id` needs to have `allow_global_logins=false` in their channel settings\n * Either leave `channel_ids` empty to use the current channel or give the list of channels we grant access"
      },
      "response": [],
      "createdAt": "2024-06-21T21:38:52.000Z",
      "updatedAt": "2024-06-21T21:38:52.000Z",
      "uid": "34196123-a6bc4962-6364-428b-968e-1f839fac368d"
    },
